"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In principle, any industry that generates data is the application scenario of the predictor.\\n\\nDue to the characteristics of blockchain, smart contracts cannot actively obtain data outside the chain, and many businesses, such as financial derivatives trading platform, lending platform, IoT, gambling games, insurance, prediction market, need to interact with the outside world. To solve such problems, predictive machines are introduced to support the realization of business.\\n\\nFor example, DeFi needs to obtain real-time currency prices of the external world through external services.Â Casino games and other scenarios need to use unpredictable, verifiable random numbers on the chain, block chain within the territory of the need to meet this demand, and through the predictor to obtain VRF verifiable random numbers can solve this problem.\",\"timestamp\":1641278523,\"title\":\"Under what circumstances is the prophecy machine used?\"},\"digest\":\"0lFANMaCJAMR7U4AdMavATGSV87ixVlrlxA88onZcS8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x94C48882C8deF8B325b2dCA7C1AafC03ED745f08\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6zMnYOPa0fpYi86PoLHIlvM-DQZlLtnQk0to4cmMZ-g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RpgsFDC1dWkJE-eUZPR-7zaVapbwspTmO3qWy3Up-v8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Xhm5dUnBVjQY7_u3ieUzKaXqsQmuMmghilycMwLyeIxZkWP0GPrwKHXpXZaXiVx6At8K76c2yuGv_g_TEsTACQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x488a8be171ec19c2fc5a4644b32a42041dde5237a4c6ad29afc0c477bb9e6c2b557c736946724647511c1bb7c81c221974dee26e65f81bf4e6f747798f53886d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6zMnYOPa0fpYi86PoLHIlvM-DQZlLtnQk0to4cmMZ-g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RpgsFDC1dWkJE-eUZPR-7zaVapbwspTmO3qWy3Up-v8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\